OL,3,CResidents warn council's new
OL,4,Cpedestrian crossing design could put
OL,5,Clives at risk
OL,7,FThe intersection in Finchampstead has
OL,8,Fbeen painted with large white leaves
OL,9,Fshowing where people can cross the
OL,10,Froads, instead of a traditional zebra
OL,11,Fcrossing design.
OL,13,FThe council removed two mini
OL,14,Froundabouts at California Crossroads
OL,15,Fand replaced them with the leaf design
OL,16,Fon the road surface.
OL,18,FWhen viewed from above, the new design
OL,19,Fon the road is more clear.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/6
