OL,3,CResidents warn council's new
OL,4,Cpedestrian crossing design could put
OL,5,Clives at risk
OL,7,FHowever, some motorists say that
OL,8,Fwithout an obvious roundabout centre
OL,9,Fto move around, vehicles are cutting
OL,10,Fstraight across to make their turns
OL,11,Fand many are not aware that the white
OL,12,Fpainted leaves are the pedestrian
OL,13,Fcrossings.
OL,15,FReuben Miles-Brar, a local shop-owner,
OL,16,Fsaid: "Previously there were two
OL,17,Froundabouts and they've decided to
OL,18,Feradicate them and add in these
OL,19,Fleaves. I've seen children trying to
OL,20,Fjump across the maple leaves thinking
OL,21,Fit is hopscotch.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/6
