OL,7,F"Just a minute ago, as I pulled up, it
OL,8,Fwas chaos here with three cars. No-one
OL,9,Fknows where they're meant to be, and
OL,10,Fthey are pulling up next to one
OL,11,Fanother and shouting at one another
OL,12,Fthrough their windows. It causes chaos
OL,13,Fand frustration."
OL,15,FLocal driving instructor, Andrew Rock,
OL,16,Ffrom X-tra Mile Academy, also has
OL,17,Fconcerns.
