OL,5,Clives at risk
OL,7,FHe said: "Even as instructors, some of
OL,8,Fus have come here and it is not always
OL,9,Fquite clear whether or not it is a
OL,10,Fcrossing, who gives way and who has
OL,11,Fpriority.
OL,13,F"Safety is one of the crucial things
OL,14,Fwe have to address when teaching and
OL,15,Fif there is any ambiguity, it makes it
OL,16,Fvery difficult for the pupils to know
OL,17,Fwhat to do and how to teach them."
