OL,3,CResidents warn council's new
OL,4,Cpedestrian crossing design could put
OL,5,Clives at risk
OL,7,FWokingham Borough Council said: "There
OL,8,Fare always concerns when a new
OL,9,Fjunction layout is introduced and we
OL,10,Funderstand that, but this scheme has
OL,11,Ffollowed Department for Transport
OL,12,Fsafety standards throughout and, as
OL,13,Flong as drivers are careful and follow
OL,14,Fthe highway code as they should, the
OL,15,Fjunction will be as safe as any other."
OL,17,FIn the coming months, the council will
OL,18,Fmonitor the road to see if any safety
OL,19,Fimprovements are needed.
